---
title: Grilled Shawarma Tofu and Golden Rice with Cucumber Salad and Spicy Tahini Sauce
description: Fire up your grill and clear your schedule to enjoy this Middle Eastern-inspired recipe. Golden rice, studded with sweet peppers is the base to smoky grilled shawarma-spiced tofu, generously drizzled with an unexpectedly addicting spicy tahini sauce!
