1 unit(s) Tofu
¾ cup Basmati Rice
1 unit(s) Sweet Bell Pepper
2 unit(s) Mini Cucumber
1 unit(s) Tomato
2 tbsp Tahini Sauce
2 tbsp Spicy Mayo
1.5 tsp Cumin-Turmeric Spice Blend
½ tbsp Shawarma Spice Blend
1 tbsp Vegetable Stock Powder
½ tbsp White Wine Vinegar
1 tbsp Butter*
1.5 tbsp Oil*
¼ tsp Sugar*
¼ tsp Salt*
¼ tsp Pepper*

Add stock powder, Cumin-Turmeric Spice Blend, 1 tbsp (2 tbsp) butter, 1 1/4 cups (2 1/2 cups) water and 1/8 tsp (1/4 tsp) salt to a medium pot. Cover and bring to a boil over high heat.
Once boiling, add rice, then reduce heat to low. Cover and cook until rice is tender and liquid is absorbed, 12-14 min.
Remove from heat. Set aside, still covered.

Meanwhile, pat tofu dry with paper towels. Cut tofu in half parallel to the cutting board. (NOTE: You will have two square tofu steaks per block.) Using a fork, poke tofu all over.
Add tofu, Shawarma Spice Blend, half the tahini sauce and 1/2 tbsp (1 tbsp) oil to a medium bowl. Season with salt and pepper. Toss to coat.

Thinly slice cucumber.
Cut tomato into 1/4-inch pieces.
Quarter, then remove core from peppers.
Add spicy mayo and remaining tahini sauce to a small bowl. Season with salt and pepper. Stir to combine, then set aside.
Add peppers and 1/2 tbsp (1 tbsp) oil to a medium bowl. Season with salt and pepper. Toss to coat, then set aside.

Add half the vinegar (use all for 4 ppl), 1/4 tsp (1/2 tsp) sugar and 1/2 tbsp (1 tbsp) oil to a large bowl. Season with salt and pepper. Stir to combine.
Add cucumber and tomato, then toss to coat. Set aside.

Add tofu to one side of the grill. Close lid and grill tofu, flipping once, until grill marked, 4-5 min per side.
Add peppers to other side of the grill. Close lid and grill until lightly charred and tender, 4-6 min per side.
Once cooked, transfer tofu and peppers to a plate. (TIP: If peppers are too charred, carefully remove the skin.)

Cut grilled peppers into 1/2-inch pieces.
Thinly slice tofu.
Fluff rice with a fork. Stir in grilled peppers and any juices from the plate.
Divide rice, tofu and veggies between plates.
Drizzle spicy tahini sauce over tofu.